      "totalCount": 4368,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40315793&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1762&rangeEnd=1815",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0632c2072672b91d060472?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1762&rangeEnd=1815"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40315793_15_115270-115321",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "115270-115321",
      "markText": "“活到这个年龄了，想起过去许多糟心事，当时桩桩件件，都觉得事情挺大，挺不过去了，现在想想，都是扯淡。”",
      "totalCount": 4332,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40315793&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=115270&rangeEnd=115321",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0632c2072672b91d060472?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=115270&rangeEnd=115321"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40315793_3_2579-2642",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2579-2642",
      "markText": "六叔指着算命的老董，这个老董，胡说了一辈子。又说，有眼人解决不了的难题，只能找瞎子了；又说，正经解决不了的问题，只能找胡说了。",
      "totalCount": 3600,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40315793&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2579&rangeEnd=2642",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0632c2072672b91d060472?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2579&rangeEnd=2642"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40315793_15_145113-145180",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "145113-145180",
      "markText": "明亮猛地惊醒，看窗外，月光如水。再想起花二娘在梦中说的话，虽然不知道这个附在花二娘身上的人是谁，但突然明白他患的什么病，吓出一身冷汗。",
      "totalCount": 3294,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40315793&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=145113&rangeEnd=145180",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0632c2072672b91d060472?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=145113&rangeEnd=145180"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40315793_6_5425-5495",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5425-5495",
      "markText": "就像羊圈里的羊，一只羊被吴大嘴杀了，其他羊惊恐一会儿，“咩咩”叫几声，又会安静地低头吃草。或者，自个儿没被抓之前，只能安静地吃草，怕也没用。",
      "totalCount": 3204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40315793&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5425&rangeEnd=5495",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0632c2072672b91d060472?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5425&rangeEnd=5495"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40315793_6_1477-1504",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1477-1504",
      "markText": "事情知道了就行了，何必说呢？事情干就是了，何必啰唆呢？",
