      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40315793&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1477&rangeEnd=1504",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0632c2072672b91d060472?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1477&rangeEnd=1504"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40315793_15_22687-22764",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "22687-22764",
      "markText": "几十年之后明亮才知道，这个“空”当时没对奶奶喷，一辈子就没人喷了，也没机会喷了；“空”不喷出去，压到心底，就成了一辈子无法告人的心事。那时明亮叹了一口气。",
      "totalCount": 3003,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40315793&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=22687&rangeEnd=22764",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0632c2072672b91d060472?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=22687&rangeEnd=22764"
    },
    {
