    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40315793_7_528-596",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "528-596",
      "markText": "“该吃吃，该喝喝，有事别往心里搁；人的命，天注定，胡思乱想没有用；天不怕，地不怕，天塌下来砸大家；该吃吃，该喝喝，你还能把我咋着？……”",
      "totalCount": 2618,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40315793&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=528&rangeEnd=596",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0632c2072672b91d060472?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=528&rangeEnd=596"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40315793_5_6489-6527",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "6489-6527",
      "markText": "没想到一件事引出了另一件事；结婚几年后，这种一件事引出另一件事的事越来越多；",
      "totalCount": 2580,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40315793&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6489&rangeEnd=6527",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d0632c2072672b91d060472?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6489&rangeEnd=6527"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40315793_4_2233-2288",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2233-2288",
